 The cr cycle ended. He did not know how long he had been in there. When he 
emerged he saw war.."So what has happened." "I had a talk with your crush or 
our leader if you perfer. Sorry boss I really think your searching for 
trouble here. Get out while you can."
  Destructor didnt change his face. "I was not concerned with that. Momentary 
weakness that never should have accured. I was refering to the ark."
   "No word yet sir. Famine and peastelens have been bring materials back and 
forth from the base."
     "Good I'll return to tha ark. And you will remain here in my place for 
know. You know my feeling on the matters at hand. If need be express them."
   He left the base in a hurry never looking back. He was unsure if he could 
ever go back. But that bridge he would cross when he had to.
